  "prompt": "In a dance class of 20 students, 20% enrolled in contemporary dance, 25% of the remaining enrolled in jazz dance, and the rest enrolled in hip-hop dance. What percentage of the entire students enrolled in hip-hop dance?\n\nShow your work briefly and put the final answer in \\boxed{}.",
